{"tid":2327943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店waddy store賣淘寶野&介紹藍酒店 推到佢道歉","createTime":"2020-12-16T10:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T10:28:14.000Z","uid":41971,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b3aec5808bedd6e827010c4ff87a2bb5a16e93b9","tid":2327943,"uid":41971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"性用品黃店waddy store賣大量淘寶野？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2326059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2326059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（整合）性用品黃店waddy store賣大量淘寶野（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2326847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2326847</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">推到佢道歉<br />\n<br />\n推到佢道歉<br />\n<br />\n推到佢道歉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n詳細點賣淘寶野再呃人係歐洲日本香港正貨 大家可以睇反上面兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋喺黃色經濟圈 唔係黃色水魚圈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次感謝碌鳩曉轉彎巴打發現佢地個page係有介紹埋藍酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ygsx96v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgsx96v.png&h=66393c12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiKgSjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiKgSjR.png&h=e375b955&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPgZP6w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPgZP6w.png&h=cb14f121&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FZ41db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FZ41db.png&h=6a445ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssyUDZS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssyUDZ